data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#ZdExportPDFModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2531485\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2531485\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 07, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104qzj1665702739109.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qzj1665702739109.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qzj1665702739109.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"qzj1665702739109\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                 \n Manually Creating and Deleting Uniface Router and Server Accounts\n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body taskbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">If the installer was unable to create accounts for the Uniface Server and Uniface Router on Microsoft Windows, you can manually create these accounts.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section context\" id=\"qzj1665702739109__context_w1707ab1b5b1_w1708ab1b5_w1709ab1\">\n<div class=\"div context\" id=\"qzj1665702739109__topic_d65573e1_d65574e1_d65575e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qzj1665702739109__p_d65576e1_d65577e1_d65578e1\">Account creation may fail, for example, if the account already exists with a different password, or if your system required passwords to conform to a specific pattern or length.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qzj1665702739109__p_d65579e1_d65580e1_d65581e1\">Even if the accounts were created, you may want to change the passwords to something that is more secure. In this case, you need to delete the accounts and recreate them with the new password.</p>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section><ol class=\"ol steps\"><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"qzj1665702739109__li_d28511e1_d28512e1_d28513e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Open a command prompt and navigate to the <span class=\"ph filepath\">common/bin</span> directory of your Uniface installation. For example:\n <kbd class=\"ph userinput\">cd /Uniface10/common/bin</kbd>\n</span>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"qzj1665702739109__li_d28514e1_d28515e1_d28516e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\" id=\"qzj1665702739109__p_d65582e1_d65583e1_d65584e1\">If you are changing the password of an existing\n               account, run the <span class=\"ph filepath\">urouter.exe</span> executable with the\n                  <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/delacc</span> switch. For example, to delete the default Uniface\n               Server account:  </span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<p class=\"p\">Enterprise Edition: <kbd class=\"ph userinput\">urouter/delacc userver</kbd></p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qzj1665702739109__p_d65585e1_d65586e1_d65587e1\">Community\n                  Edition: <kbd class=\"ph userinput\">urouter/delacc UnifaceServer</kbd>\n</p>\n</div>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"qzj1665702739109__li_d28517e1_d28518e1_d28519e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Run the <span class=\"ph filepath\">urouter.exe</span> executable with the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/newacc</span> switch and optional parameters. For example:\n </span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">urouter/newacc userver /passwd my2userv&amp;c</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"qzj1665702739109__li_d28520e1_d28521e1_d28522e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\" id=\"qzj1665702739109__p_d65588e1_d65589e1_d65590e1\">If you have specified a different password for\n               the Uniface Server account, modify the associated password in\n                  <span class=\"ph filepath\">web.xml</span>, and in any assignment files where it is\n               specified.</span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<p class=\"p\">For example, in <span class=\"ph filepath\">web.xml</span>, edit the\n                     <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">MIDDLEWARE</span> parameter:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">&lt;init-param&gt;\n &lt;param-name&gt;MIDDLEWARE&lt;/param-name&gt;\n &lt;param-value&gt;UV8:localhost+13003|userver|my2userv&amp;c|wasv&lt;/param-value&gt;\n&lt;/init-param&gt;</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</li></ol></section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tsv1665702739177.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>/delacc</a><p>Delete a Uniface Router or Uniface Server account on Windows platforms.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fvp1665702738973.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>/newacc</a><p>Create a new account on Windows platforms for the Uniface Router or Uniface Server.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tfr1665702739041.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>/passwd</a><p>Creates a password for the newly created Uniface Server or Uniface Router account.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531485\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531485\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Manually Creating and Deleting Uniface Router and Server Accounts Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 07, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Manually Creating and Deleting Uniface Router and Server Accounts If the installer was unable to create accounts for the Uniface Server and Uniface Router on Microsoft Windows, you can manually create these accounts. Account creation may fail, for example, if the account already exists with a different password, or if your system required passwords to conform to a specific pattern or length. Even if the accounts were created, you may want to change the passwords to something that is more secure. In this case, you need to delete the accounts and recreate them with the new password. Open a command prompt and navigate to the common/bin directory of your Uniface installation. For example: cd /Uniface10/common/bin If you are changing the password of an existing account, run the urouter.exe executable with the /delacc switch. For example, to delete the default Uniface Server account: Enterprise Edition: urouter/delacc userver Community Edition: urouter/delacc UnifaceServer Run the urouter.exe executable with the /newacc switch and optional parameters. For example: urouter/newacc userver /passwd my2userv&c Copy If you have specified a different password for the Uniface Server account, modify the associated password in web.xml , and in any assignment files where it is specified. For example, in web.xml , edit the MIDDLEWARE parameter: <init-param> <param-name>MIDDLEWARE</param-name> <param-value>UV8:localhost+13003|userver|my2userv&c|wasv</param-value> </init-param> Copy Related Links /delacc Delete a Uniface Router or Uniface Server account on Windows platforms. /newacc Create a new account on Windows platforms for the Uniface Router or Uniface Server. /passwd Creates a password for the newly created Uniface Server or Uniface Router account. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}